= Mateusz Winiarski

Mateusz 'the Black' Winiarski is a Krośnian SMP revolutionary. He is known from his strong belief regarding Linux supremacy. 

# actions: fundraising, organizing workers, inter-party relations, clear the agenda
# actions: transportation ministry, industrial ministry, relations with WRSS, ddd

